title: Jamie Dornan & Dakota Johnson Try to Make Furniture Instructions Sound Sexy! (Video)
text:
Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson are pretty much experts on sexy after filming the full Fifty Shades franchise, but can they make furniture instructions sound sexy?
In a fun video filmed at the press junket for Fifty Shades Darker recently, the two stars were challenged by ET Canada to make the boring instructions sound as sexy as possible.
The movie is set to hit theaters this Friday (February 10) and we have already been given a sneak peek of the scene in which Christian Grey proposes to Anastasia Steele . Make sure to go watch it now!
